Description_lang: Aimed Shot, Rapid Fire, and Arcane Shot now hit a second nearby target for $s1% of their damage.

description_blz.en_US: Aimed Shot, Rapid Fire, and Arcane Shot now hit a second nearby target for 60% of their damage.
